               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 3ra-76ra, 78rb-82rb)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-6va)&#xD;
I-2) Taʾāmra Māryām: 76 miracles (fols. 6va-8va, 11va-76ra, 78rb-82rb)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki … “I worship Thee…” (fols. 8va-9rb l.5)&#xD;
I-4) Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 9rb l.6-11rb)&#xD;
I-5) ʾAkkonu bǝʾǝsi… “Does not the man…” (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols. 12va-48ra)&#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Mikāʾel “Miracles of Michael”: 4 miracles (fols. 76ra-78rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
